com.facebook.buck.apple

Class AppleDebuggableBinary

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.AbstractBuildRule
      • com.facebook.buck.apple.AppleDebuggableBinary
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BuildRuleWithBinary, HasBuildTarget, BuildRule, HasPostBuildSteps, java.lang.Comparable<BuildRule>

    public class AppleDebuggableBinary
extends AbstractBuildRule
implements HasPostBuildSteps, BuildRuleWithBinary
    Depending on the debug type (AppleDebugFormat), it will generate appropriate debug symbols in separate build steps. In any case it will strip out the debug symbols from binary.
